==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Erecto-patent
<hw>E*rec"to-pat"ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having a position intermediate between erect and
patent, or spreading.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zo⟦oum⟧l.)</fld> <def>Standing partially spread and
erect; -- said of the wings of certain insects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Erector</ent>⟦br⟧
